    Object oMunkalap_DD is a cMunkalapDataDictionary
        Set DDO_Server To oAuto_DD
        Set DDO_Server To oUgyfel_DD
        Property Date pdStartRogzites
        Property Date pdStopRogzites

        Procedure OnConstrain 
            Date dStart dStop

            Get pdStartRogzites To dStart
            Get pdStopRogzites To dStop

            Case Begin
                Case (dStart <> 0 and dStop <> 0)
                    Constrain Munkalap.Rogzites between dStart and dStop
                    Case Break
                Case (dStart <> 0)
                    Constrain Munkalap.Rogzites GE dStart
                    Case Break
                Case (dStop <> 0)
                    Constrain Munkalap.Rogzites LE dStop
            Case End
        End_Procedure 
    End_Object 

    Set Main_DD To oMunkalap_DD



